
- Top page
  http://localhost:8888
  

- DTO / Database entities
 User
   -key
   -id (userid)
   -name (username)
   -token
   -timestamp
   
 Event
   -key
   -id (eventid)
   -title :String
   -eventDate :Date
   -place :String
   -budget :String
   -genre :String(?)
   -restaurant
   -owner :User(ownerRef)
   -participants :Array<Participant>(participantsRef)
   -timestamp :Date

 PreEvent
   -key
   -event (eventRef --> Event)
   -dates:Array (e.g. 11/23, 11/24, 11/25)
   -places:Array (e.g. Boston, NY, LA)
   -budges:Array (e.g. 1000-2000, 2000-3000, 3000-4000)
   -genres:Array (e.g. Japanese, Chinese, Western)
   -restaurants:Array (e.g. A, B, C)
 
 Response(enum)
   - OK(0), Pending(1), NG(2)

 Participant
   -key
   -event (eventRef --> Event)
   -user (userRef --> User)
   -comment :String
   -attend :Response
   -dates :Array<Response>
   -places :Array<Response>
   -budges :Array<Response>
   -genres :Array<Response>
   -restaurants :Array<Response>


- Web services
  *root: http://localhost:8888/api/v1/

 auth/facebook/
 auth/facebook/token
 
 auth/facebook/check
   service=login
 
 
 me/get
   service=me
   service=my_friends
 
 me/update
   nothing   

 event/get
   #service=all_events
   service=my_events
   service=search(keyword)
   
     offset=int(first position)
     limit=int(last position)
     withHistory=true/false

 event/update
   service=create_pre_event(title, dates, places, budgets, genres, restaurants, participants)
   service=update_pre_event(eventid, <same as above>)
   service=create_event(title, date, place, budget, genre, restaurant, participants)
   service=update_event(eventid, <same as above>)
   
   service=reply_pre_event(eventid, dates, places, budgets, genres, restaurants, comment)
   service=reply_event(eventid, attend, comment)
   service=cancel_event(eventid)
   service=add_friend([userid, userid, ....])


